n-left: auto; margin-right: auto; display: block;"></strong></p>
<p style=3D"font-weight: normal; font-size: 16px;">With over 25 years of in=
novation<span style=3D"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">, we have&nbsp;<strong>i=
ncreased our cell viability by 32%</strong>. Through our 21-day FlexCell pr=
opagation process and our packaging technology,</span>&nbsp;we are <span st=
yle=3D"font-weight: bold;">able to offer 94.9% cell viability after 6 month=
s with </span><a href=3D"https://www.whitelabs.com/research-development" re=
l=3D"noopener" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"font-weight: bold;">PurePitch<sup=
>=C2=AE</sup> Next Generation</a><span style=3D"font-weight: bold;">&nbsp;H=
omebrew</span>.</p>
